/** * Factory and utilities pertaining to the {@code MapConstraint} interface. * * @see Constraints * @author Mike Bostock * @since 3.0 * @deprecated Use {@link Preconditions} for basic checks. In place of * constrained maps, we encourage you to check your preconditions * explicitly instead of leaving that work to the map implementation. * For the specific case of rejecting null, consider {@link ImmutableMap}. * This class is scheduled for removal in Guava 20.0. */
